title: Donald Trump's Mug Shot Matters in a World of Fakes
description: The first booking photo of a US president stands out among a sea of photoshops and AI-generated images online.

title: AI Can’t Read Books. It’s Reviewing Them Anyway
description: ChatGPT-powered avatars recently gushed over a new book—unconvincingly. But if AI develops actual opinions, authors might be in for a shock.

title: The ‘Budget Ryan Reynolds’ Taking Bitcoin FC to the Big Leagues
description: Bitcoin podcaster Peter McCormack bought his local nonleague soccer team. Can he really turn Real Bedford FC into a global sports brand?

title: Trump's Prosecution Is America's Last Hope
description: Social norms—not laws—are the underlying fabric of democracy. The Georgia indictment against Donald Trump is the last remaining tool left to repair that which he’s torn apart.
